check.action:
Read the ticket file completely. Extract from frontmatter: - status (must be `ready`; halt if not) - aliases[0] → {{ticket_alias}} - tags[0] → {{primary_tag}} (must be one of feature/bug/ exploration/hotfix/infrastructure/chore; halt if not) - topic → {{ticket_topic}}
Derive {{ticket_slug}} from the ticket_alias (strip the `ticket-YYYY-MM-DD-` prefix).
Store {{ticket_path}} = absolute path to the ticket file.
